sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthSrv as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Dashboard Access
    User->>Router: GET / <br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>OAuthSrv: OAuth Authentication Flow<br/>HTTPS/6443
    OAuthSrv-->>OAuth: OAuth Token
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Backend-->>OAuth: HTML/JS Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>User: Dashboard UI

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Dashboard API to Kubernetes
    User->>Router: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Router->>OAuth: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook Created
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>User: Success Response

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 3: Metrics Query
    User->>Router: GET /api/prometheus/query<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Router->>OAuth: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: GET /api/prometheus/query<br/>HTTP/8080
    Backend->>Prom: Query Metrics<br/>HTTPS/9092<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Prom-->>Backend: Metrics Data
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>User: Metrics Data

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: WebSocket Communication
    User->>Router: WebSocket Upgrade<br/>wss://dashboard/ws
    Router->>OAuth: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>Backend: WebSocket Connection<br/>HTTP/8080 Upgrade<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch Resources<br/>WebSocket/6443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Resource Updates (Stream)
    Backend-->>OAuth: WebSocket Messages
    OAuth-->>Router: WebSocket Messages
    Router-->>User: Live Updates
